WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.920
=Episode 13=

01:45.360 --> 01:46.960
Distinguished leaders and guests,

01:46.960 --> 01:47.641
good day.

01:47.761 --> 01:50.401
(Strategic Cooperation Signing Ceremony)
This is the venue

01:50.481 --> 01:53.080
for Jinda Group and Shifeng Group's
strategic cooperation signing.

01:53.281 --> 01:56.281
First, let's give
a warm round of applause

01:56.401 --> 01:58.921
to extend our most sincere welcome
to all the leaders

01:59.041 --> 02:00.841
and guests present here today.

02:01.080 --> 02:02.041
Welcome!

02:06.600 --> 02:07.041
Alright,

02:07.160 --> 02:10.081
now please welcome
the two representatives to the stage.

02:10.241 --> 02:13.320
Mr. Shen Jinsong,
Chairman of Jinda Group,

02:13.521 --> 02:16.200
and Mr. Zheng Yuanzhou,
Chairman of Shifeng Group,

02:16.521 --> 02:17.801
please come forward to sign.

02:17.961 --> 02:18.681
Applause please.

02:27.361 --> 02:27.801
Very well.

02:27.880 --> 02:30.640
Both representatives,
please hold the ceremonial pens.

02:31.640 --> 02:33.241
Three, two, one.

02:33.361 --> 02:34.961
Please sign the documents.

02:38.880 --> 02:39.600
Hold on!

02:41.160 --> 02:42.160
A moment if I may.

02:45.561 --> 02:46.200
Zheng Yuanzhou,

02:46.801 --> 02:48.480
during Shifeng Group's board election,

02:48.600 --> 02:50.640
you unlawfully
obtained votes and benefits

02:50.880 --> 02:51.801
through bribery, etc.

02:52.121 --> 02:53.801
Your actions
constitute suspected bribery.

02:55.681 --> 02:56.480
Here is the warrant.

02:57.681 --> 02:58.320
Read it.

02:59.600 --> 03:00.880
Come with us for investigation.

03:01.241 --> 03:01.801
Cuff him.

03:09.920 --> 03:10.640
Step aside.

03:13.760 --> 03:14.841
Step aside.

03:15.841 --> 03:16.561
Please make way.

03:20.144 --> 03:21.509
(Shen)

03:22.681 --> 03:23.160
Mr. Shen,

03:23.320 --> 03:26.241
the news of our impending cooperation
with Shifeng was released early.

03:26.480 --> 03:28.361
When Mr. Zheng's scandal broke,

03:28.561 --> 03:30.681
our stock price started plummeting
at market open.

03:31.001 --> 03:32.961
If there's no recovery by tomorrow,

03:33.440 --> 03:35.920
shareholders will likely
convene an emergency board meeting.

03:38.681 --> 03:39.320
I see.

03:42.760 --> 03:43.320
Mr. Shen.

03:44.561 --> 03:44.920
Dad.

03:45.081 --> 03:45.681
Don't call me.

03:47.361 --> 03:47.920
Go home.

03:51.521 --> 03:53.640
I came to report something important.

03:54.600 --> 03:57.561
Zheng Yuanzhou's
bribery-fueled chairmanship election

03:58.241 --> 04:00.640
has destroyed his reputation.

04:01.081 --> 04:03.160
Shifeng Group
can't escape the fallout either.

04:03.440 --> 04:04.920
Several agreed-upon projects

04:05.561 --> 04:08.040
are now facing withdrawal
from key partners.

04:08.760 --> 04:10.920
I've decided to collaborate with Shouke

04:11.440 --> 04:12.681
to reclaim those projects.

04:12.961 --> 04:14.081
That's preposterous!

04:14.681 --> 04:15.841
What's the point of that?

04:16.241 --> 04:16.960
We have no land.

04:17.880 --> 04:19.200
Shouke and I secured it

04:19.640 --> 04:20.400
through bidding.

04:23.001 --> 04:24.801
Land acquisition requires funds.

04:25.121 --> 04:26.320
Where's your money?

04:27.041 --> 04:28.001
Yuanhang Fund.

04:28.801 --> 04:29.520
Yuanhang?

04:33.921 --> 04:35.041
These people and affairs

04:36.241 --> 04:38.280
couldn't have been achieved overnight.

04:39.921 --> 04:42.681
Unless you had a long-term,
meticulous plan

04:42.960 --> 04:44.241
already in motion.

04:45.760 --> 04:47.601
Even with such a plan,

04:48.280 --> 04:51.080
if Zheng hadn't imploded,

04:51.280 --> 04:52.840
it couldn't have been executed.

04:57.921 --> 04:59.440
You knew Zheng's downfall?

05:02.001 --> 05:03.320
Dad, I warned you before.

05:03.361 --> 05:04.161
You forgot.

05:05.400 --> 05:07.161
Zheng Yuanzhou has three confidants.

05:08.080 --> 05:10.200
The last-ranked one is the most capable.

05:10.561 --> 05:11.601
He overworked

05:12.320 --> 05:14.200
but didn't gain enough credit
for a long time.

05:14.681 --> 05:15.840
Resentment was inevitable.

05:20.001 --> 05:20.520
Wait.

05:20.520 --> 05:21.640
Let me confirm.

05:21.640 --> 05:23.361
You're implying

05:23.400 --> 05:26.840
that you orchestrated Zheng's downfall?

05:27.721 --> 05:30.121
Certain truths should remain
between father and son.

05:31.960 --> 05:32.880
Hold on.

05:32.960 --> 05:33.681
Move over there.

05:34.760 --> 05:35.481
Tell me.

05:35.801 --> 05:39.241
How did you secure that man's loyalty?

05:40.520 --> 05:42.440
During my London internship,

05:43.760 --> 05:45.041
I flew back five times.

05:45.481 --> 05:46.520
He avoided me each time.

05:47.840 --> 05:49.161
On the sixth attempt, he met me.

05:50.080 --> 05:51.161
We immediately aligned.

05:51.481 --> 05:52.960
All terms were agreed upon.

05:53.880 --> 05:56.640
I emphasized three points:

05:57.921 --> 05:58.640
recognition,

05:59.520 --> 06:00.280
sincerity,

06:00.760 --> 06:01.601
and benefits.

06:02.561 --> 06:05.241
I showed him my character
and convinced him

06:05.880 --> 06:06.960
that when I pursue goals,

06:07.520 --> 06:11.400
I spare no effort to achieve them.

06:22.400 --> 06:23.041
Dad,

06:24.721 --> 06:27.520
I know you've never wanted me
involved in the projects.

06:28.361 --> 06:32.520
I can now publicly announce the news
about our cooperation with Shouke

06:32.880 --> 06:34.640
and use the company's
stock price recovery

06:35.400 --> 06:37.400
to reassure shareholders.

06:37.880 --> 06:39.121
Or I can leave Jinda

06:40.001 --> 06:41.200
and work with Shouke alone.

06:44.520 --> 06:46.001
Tell me your conditions.

06:48.601 --> 06:49.200
First,

06:50.200 --> 06:52.200
I need to bring my own people
into the company.

06:52.280 --> 06:53.640
Whatever department they go,

06:54.080 --> 06:57.561
I want your decisive vote
supporting my choices.

06:57.880 --> 06:58.320
Second,

06:58.320 --> 07:00.280
I need to establish
my own independent department

07:00.520 --> 07:03.200
with full authority
over personnel and financial matters,

07:03.361 --> 07:05.041
free from any interference.

07:06.241 --> 07:07.801
I hope to gain your support.

07:17.241 --> 07:18.440
All departments, get ready.

07:18.481 --> 07:19.320
Host, get ready.

07:19.520 --> 07:20.400
Counting down.

07:20.561 --> 07:25.520
Five, four, three, two, one.

07:25.840 --> 07:27.400
(Host: Xu Yan)
The city's renowned real estate firms,

07:27.440 --> 07:31.001
Jinda Group and Shouke Real Estate,
have established strategic cooperation

07:31.400 --> 07:33.601
in jointly developing Plot 178.

07:34.041 --> 07:35.400
Both companies stated

07:35.481 --> 07:37.640
this marks a milestone collaboration,

07:37.840 --> 07:39.161
signifying that both companies

07:39.241 --> 07:42.400
have taken solid steps
in diversified development strategies

07:42.760 --> 07:46.440
while creating new opportunities
and growth potential for the industry.

07:47.320 --> 07:50.520
Jinda Group will adopt Shouke's
technology and management expertise

07:50.801 --> 07:53.721
to further enhance project quality
and service standards

07:53.840 --> 07:57.320
to provide consumers with quality,
convenient residential and commercial

07:57.361 --> 07:58.320
experiences.

07:58.880 --> 08:02.320
(Reportedly, this cooperation
was spearheaded by Shen Haoming,)

08:02.400 --> 08:05.921
(Jinda Group's Vice President
and head of the Plot 178 task force.)

08:06.561 --> 08:08.880
(He stated
that the successful agreement signing)

08:09.121 --> 08:11.921
(resulted from the company's
long-term commitment to innovation)

08:12.041 --> 08:13.520
(and deepened cooperation.)

08:14.200 --> 08:16.520
(That concludes
the latest city updates.)

08:16.561 --> 08:19.121
(We'll continue
monitoring follow-up developments)

08:19.361 --> 08:22.561
(to bring you
more comprehensive coverage.)

08:23.440 --> 08:24.681
Shen Jinsong

08:25.960 --> 08:27.161
dares not face me.

08:30.041 --> 08:30.880
Shen Haoming,

08:31.440 --> 08:32.760
you just rose to power

08:33.800 --> 08:35.640
and are finding ways to sabotage me.

08:35.841 --> 08:37.280
First you promoted me sideways,

08:37.640 --> 08:39.201
pushing me out of core departments

08:39.441 --> 08:40.560
and marginalizing me.

08:40.680 --> 08:42.520
You really are something.

08:42.841 --> 08:44.680
I watched you grow up.

08:45.520 --> 08:51.400
Is this how you
treat your father's key contributor?

08:52.760 --> 08:53.601
There's no denying

08:55.920 --> 08:57.880
you've brought the company
significant profits.

08:58.121 --> 08:59.760
But while generating revenue,

09:01.241 --> 09:02.880
plenty found its way into your pockets.

09:06.121 --> 09:07.201
You earn 3 million annually

09:08.241 --> 09:09.361
and own two villas,

09:09.441 --> 09:11.400
one with a 200-square-meter garden.

09:11.880 --> 09:12.560
You also have

09:12.880 --> 09:15.001
properties in America and Australia.

09:15.920 --> 09:16.760
Over these years,

09:16.841 --> 09:18.680
you helped my father build this empire

09:19.800 --> 09:21.121
as one of the founding pioneers.

09:21.241 --> 09:22.520
I've always respected you

09:23.081 --> 09:24.841
for your decades of dedication

09:24.841 --> 09:25.601
and hard work.

09:25.760 --> 09:30.001
But your pay has been the highest
in the industry.

09:30.160 --> 09:31.680
We haven't wronged you.

09:32.880 --> 09:34.160
What I can do is

09:35.081 --> 09:37.040
when legal authorities prosecute you,

09:38.121 --> 09:41.361
I'll demonstrate to the court
about your cooperative attitude

09:41.361 --> 09:42.640
and your voluntary compensation.

09:45.241 --> 09:46.001
Stop thinking.

09:49.441 --> 09:50.841
This is your only option.

09:53.008 --> 09:54.512
(Resignation Agreement)

10:09.721 --> 10:10.520
What brings you?

10:11.961 --> 10:13.520
I knew you were working late.

10:13.520 --> 10:16.361
So I wanted to ask you out
for late-night snacks.

10:17.601 --> 10:18.481
Since you mention it,

10:18.481 --> 10:19.520
I am actually hungry.

10:19.560 --> 10:20.880
I just need to send an email.

10:21.241 --> 10:22.520
No problem, I'll wait.

10:24.040 --> 10:24.640
Okay.

10:25.241 --> 10:25.841
Let's go.

10:27.601 --> 10:28.280
What to eat?

10:31.001 --> 10:32.081
That place from before?

10:32.321 --> 10:32.760
Okay.

10:34.800 --> 10:35.441
Haoming.

10:36.441 --> 10:37.121
Mr. Wu.

10:37.680 --> 10:39.201
Still working this late?

10:39.760 --> 10:43.640
I need to talk with you.

10:45.520 --> 10:47.001
Haoming, perhaps...

10:48.601 --> 10:49.201
Go ahead.

10:49.841 --> 10:51.400
I acknowledge my mistakes.

10:52.040 --> 10:54.601
I accept the company's punishment.

10:55.400 --> 10:59.201
But could you
consider my years of service

11:00.160 --> 11:01.361
and give me one more chance?

11:03.760 --> 11:05.001
I don't want to leave.

11:06.560 --> 11:07.241
Mr. Wu,

11:07.800 --> 11:10.920
you should've anticipated consequences
before acting.

11:11.640 --> 11:13.280
Staying with the company is impossible.

11:13.961 --> 11:14.560
Let's go.

11:16.121 --> 11:16.760
Haoming,

11:18.640 --> 11:20.361
my wife left me
and took the kids with her.

11:20.640 --> 11:21.961
I got nothing in the divorce.

11:22.800 --> 11:23.920
Being fired at my age,

11:24.441 --> 11:25.400
if this gets out,

11:26.321 --> 11:27.321
I will be ruined

11:27.361 --> 11:29.160
and no company would ever hire me again.

11:29.560 --> 11:32.121
Even my own wife and kids
look down on me.

11:34.481 --> 11:35.201
I'm sorry.

11:37.160 --> 11:37.760
Haoming,

11:38.280 --> 11:39.760
I've truly lost everything.

11:40.680 --> 11:41.721
Please have some mercy

11:42.560 --> 11:44.201
and let me stay in the company.

11:44.841 --> 11:47.920
Even a meaningless position would do.

11:49.800 --> 11:51.961
I've truly lost everything.

11:53.201 --> 11:53.841
Mr. Wu,

11:54.800 --> 11:56.680
consider it early retirement.

11:57.880 --> 11:59.601
The company
can't make exceptions for this.

12:00.160 --> 12:00.640
Let's go.

12:05.841 --> 12:06.481
Haoming.

12:08.241 --> 12:08.880
Haoming!

12:14.841 --> 12:15.481
Are you okay?

12:15.560 --> 12:16.201
I'm fine.

12:23.880 --> 12:25.241
Seems you really need to retire.

12:26.601 --> 12:27.481
Let me go!

12:28.601 --> 12:29.321
You alright?

12:47.344 --> 12:48.436
(Fang Lei)

13:15.441 --> 13:16.441
Back so early?

13:20.880 --> 13:21.760
How's your injury?

13:22.640 --> 13:24.040
I'm fine. Don't worry.

13:24.160 --> 13:24.800
Let me see.

13:27.241 --> 13:27.841
Haoming.

13:28.001 --> 13:32.201
I got you a supplementary card.

13:33.160 --> 13:35.001
No spending limit. Use it freely.

13:38.321 --> 13:39.481
What's this reward for?

13:39.601 --> 13:42.081
Go shopping after you recover.

13:42.321 --> 13:43.481
Buy whatever you like.

13:45.481 --> 13:46.560
I don't want this.

13:47.001 --> 13:48.760
You must keep the card.

13:48.961 --> 13:49.400
Here.

13:49.520 --> 13:50.560
There are more to come.

13:52.640 --> 13:53.920
That's not what I meant.

13:58.841 --> 13:59.321
Hello?

14:01.680 --> 14:02.321
I see.

14:02.841 --> 14:03.640
I'm coming over now.

14:06.241 --> 14:07.201
It's about Wu Deliang.

14:07.520 --> 14:08.721
I need to go to the office.

14:12.241 --> 14:13.361
Will you be back for dinner?

14:13.760 --> 14:14.280
Sure.

14:14.760 --> 14:15.400
Order takeout.

14:15.680 --> 14:16.601
Don't cook yourself.

14:18.961 --> 14:19.961
I'll wait for you.

14:44.081 --> 14:44.601
Mr. Fang,

14:44.601 --> 14:45.680
long time no see.

14:46.520 --> 14:47.961
How have you been in America?

14:48.481 --> 14:49.121
Pretty well.

14:50.841 --> 14:51.880
I came back this time

14:52.081 --> 14:54.321
mainly for the New District project
you're handling.

14:54.520 --> 14:55.680
Lei told me everything.

14:56.481 --> 14:59.121
Your return
couldn't have come at a better time.

14:59.841 --> 15:03.160
The New District project's funding
relies entirely on you now.

15:03.880 --> 15:04.601
Haoming,

15:06.081 --> 15:07.321
I know your capabilities.

15:07.721 --> 15:09.280
For the final signing phase,

15:09.560 --> 15:11.201
I'll lend my support.

15:12.400 --> 15:13.441
Thank you, Mr. Fang.

15:13.680 --> 15:17.201
Has Lei been any trouble at Jinda Group?

15:17.800 --> 15:18.241
Not at all.

15:18.640 --> 15:21.640
Lei's the only daughter I have left.

15:22.081 --> 15:24.081
Please continue looking after her.

15:25.001 --> 15:27.760
Fang Lei's been calling me 'brother'
since her teens.

15:28.241 --> 15:29.201
Now that she's back,

15:29.361 --> 15:30.880
it's right that I

15:31.280 --> 15:32.160
care for her.

15:35.920 --> 15:39.920
Shame Fang Yu left us too soon.

15:48.920 --> 15:50.081
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

15:50.081 --> 15:51.001
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

15:51.160 --> 15:51.961
Goodbye.

15:52.280 --> 15:53.361
Son, over here.

15:55.680 --> 15:56.880
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:56.880 --> 15:57.560
Haoming!

15:58.081 --> 15:59.400
What brings you here?

16:00.961 --> 16:02.760
Since when
do you have time to pick me up?

16:02.920 --> 16:04.560
Thought I was seeing things.

16:04.680 --> 16:05.400
What do you want?

16:05.441 --> 16:06.121
I'll take you.

16:07.160 --> 16:08.560
Burgers, fried chicken, and fries.

16:09.640 --> 16:11.201
Where to after eating?

16:12.040 --> 16:13.201
Are you free today?

16:13.441 --> 16:14.680
I'm all yours today.

16:15.160 --> 16:16.280
Really?

16:17.241 --> 16:19.361
It's not my birthday, is it?

16:22.721 --> 16:23.952
- Seatbelt.
- Okay.

16:29.961 --> 16:31.920
Let's play a game.

16:32.241 --> 16:33.121
What game?

16:33.680 --> 16:36.361
I want to create
a fantasy football team.

16:36.520 --> 16:37.721
You have two options each time

16:37.721 --> 16:38.640
and need to pick one.

16:38.760 --> 16:39.280
Deal.

16:41.560 --> 16:43.001
First, the goalkeeper.

16:45.481 --> 16:47.841
Buffon or Kahn?

16:49.481 --> 16:50.880
Isn't Kahn

16:51.321 --> 16:51.961
the captain?

16:52.361 --> 16:53.001
What?

16:53.400 --> 16:54.081
Well...

16:54.081 --> 16:55.400
Right, he's Germany's captain.

16:55.721 --> 16:58.721
No, Kahn is English.

17:01.880 --> 17:04.001
I confused him with that striker.

17:04.681 --> 17:05.840
Exactly. What's funny?

17:06.161 --> 17:07.040
The striker,

17:07.161 --> 17:07.681
Messi,

17:08.161 --> 17:08.681
right?

17:08.721 --> 17:09.360
Okay.

17:09.961 --> 17:10.840
Let's do it tomorrow.

17:10.840 --> 17:11.161
Okay.

17:11.681 --> 17:13.001
- Sleep. It's late.
- Haoming.

17:13.320 --> 17:15.320
Let's do this often from now on, okay?

17:16.961 --> 17:17.320
Deal.

17:18.600 --> 17:19.120
Sleep.

17:20.080 --> 17:21.840
Let's team up every night.

17:22.921 --> 17:24.560
First decide between Ronaldo and Messi.

17:24.560 --> 17:25.280
Then tell me.

17:26.201 --> 17:27.320
Think carefully.

17:27.320 --> 17:28.881
It's the ultimate dilemma.

17:29.481 --> 17:29.921
True.

17:30.520 --> 17:31.120
Bedtime.

17:48.560 --> 17:50.928
(Yan)

17:51.320 --> 17:52.600
Are you leaving again?

17:54.080 --> 17:54.641
No.

17:55.520 --> 17:56.360
I'm staying.

17:56.400 --> 17:57.456
(Yan)

17:58.032 --> 18:00.112
(Haoming)

18:02.982 --> 18:05.552
(Haoming)

18:12.721 --> 18:15.320
(A woman's sixth sense tells me
there's a crisis approaching.)

18:16.320 --> 18:19.080
(I sense that sandcastle we built)

18:20.201 --> 18:21.881
(is gradually collapsing)

18:23.161 --> 18:24.120
(and crumbling.)

18:29.721 --> 18:30.600
Dear viewers,

18:30.600 --> 18:34.840
we've finally located
this hidden noodle shop in the alley.

18:35.001 --> 18:36.921
Let's find out together what makes

18:36.921 --> 18:38.681
this 30-year-old noodle shop so special.

18:38.840 --> 18:41.560
I'll be your taste tester today.

18:45.641 --> 18:49.080
The noodles have a wonderfully chewy
and springy texture.

18:49.241 --> 18:49.881
Siwei,

18:50.600 --> 18:51.800
take another bite.

18:52.040 --> 18:52.961
A big mouthful.

18:57.080 --> 18:58.120
I can't resist

18:58.120 --> 18:59.641
wanting another big bite.

19:01.040 --> 19:02.560
Cut! Stop!

19:06.401 --> 19:09.641
Mom, I'm begging you.

19:10.080 --> 19:12.201
Get me a different job, please?

19:13.840 --> 19:14.600
I...

19:17.401 --> 19:19.280
I can't take this anymore.

19:19.320 --> 19:21.161
I'm filming outdoor segments daily,

19:21.201 --> 19:22.721
eating at 7 to 8 restaurants per day.

19:22.721 --> 19:24.001
I'm gonna puke!

19:24.800 --> 19:25.721
Sun Siwei,

19:25.921 --> 19:26.800
listen to me.

19:26.921 --> 19:27.881
No way.

19:27.961 --> 19:28.961
We can't support you.

19:30.320 --> 19:32.161
What's more important? Me or money?

19:32.520 --> 19:33.560
Money!

19:34.560 --> 19:35.320
Mom?

19:41.401 --> 19:42.441
Siwei, hurry up.

19:42.721 --> 19:43.721
Next shop's waiting.

19:44.241 --> 19:44.800
Coming.

19:53.921 --> 19:55.001
Forget anniversaries.

19:55.161 --> 19:55.840
Not even gifts

19:55.961 --> 19:57.080
for birthdays.

19:57.201 --> 19:58.401
Always 'forgot' when asked.

19:59.001 --> 20:00.600
Oh god, same with mine.

20:00.600 --> 20:02.681
He literally doesn't see me at all.

20:02.681 --> 20:03.721
He only cares about work.

20:03.760 --> 20:04.481
Oh my.

20:05.280 --> 20:06.481
It's not worth it at all.

20:06.481 --> 20:07.040
Exactly.

20:07.080 --> 20:07.881
Can you believe it?

20:08.201 --> 20:09.280
Same thing last night.

20:09.280 --> 20:09.921
Morning, Yan.

20:10.201 --> 20:10.721
Morning, Yan.

20:10.721 --> 20:11.201
Morning.

20:11.520 --> 20:12.881
Your guy's the best.

20:12.881 --> 20:13.320
Yan,

20:13.360 --> 20:14.201
- the files you wanted.
- Every day

20:14.320 --> 20:15.520
he picks you up after work.

20:15.560 --> 20:17.001
Don't get me started on him.

20:17.120 --> 20:18.520
He has no sense of style

20:18.560 --> 20:19.681
and no career ambition.

20:20.080 --> 20:21.241
A total clueless big man,

20:21.360 --> 20:22.401
immune to romance.

20:22.721 --> 20:23.881
After coming home,

20:24.120 --> 20:25.600
he doesn't say a word to me.

20:25.921 --> 20:26.441
Really?

20:26.441 --> 20:27.241
He's useless.

20:27.721 --> 20:29.401
Yan, you're the real champion.

20:29.921 --> 20:31.040
With privileged background,

20:31.161 --> 20:31.840
you work hard

20:32.161 --> 20:33.600
and have earned your top spot.

20:33.961 --> 20:35.560
You even married an amazing husband.

20:36.161 --> 20:37.560
You live a charmed life.

20:38.520 --> 20:39.481
No kidding.

20:39.600 --> 20:41.241
Your husband keeps sending gifts.

20:41.360 --> 20:45.001
Is the proposal for
our planning meeting ready?

20:45.641 --> 20:46.641
Right away.

20:46.721 --> 20:47.881
We're working on it now.

20:49.481 --> 20:50.280
Jiang Lai,

20:51.120 --> 20:52.600
is this the script you wrote?

20:53.280 --> 20:54.441
Have you read it yourself?

20:54.560 --> 20:55.681
Is it human language?

20:57.520 --> 20:58.840
Sorry. I'll revise it.

21:17.401 --> 21:19.001
I've reviewed your field recording.

21:20.401 --> 21:21.401
You seemed uneasy eating.

21:22.681 --> 21:23.721
What'd the audience think?

21:25.040 --> 21:26.280
Will they find it interesting?

21:29.001 --> 21:29.800
I tried my best.

21:30.921 --> 21:33.241
I've never eaten cheap noodles
since childhood.

21:33.320 --> 21:34.921
How happy did you expect me to look?

21:35.401 --> 21:36.520
The audience is smart

21:36.520 --> 21:37.481
and sensitive.

21:38.360 --> 21:41.201
So don't patronize them
with your half-hearted efforts.

21:43.320 --> 21:44.641
For the next episode's video,

21:45.280 --> 21:46.201
I need you

21:47.120 --> 21:49.401
to show sincerity in every single frame.

21:59.080 --> 22:00.961
Stop wearing heels
during field recordings.

22:01.681 --> 22:02.481
Wear sneakers.

22:02.721 --> 22:03.520
They're convenient.

22:04.040 --> 22:05.800
Heels slow down filming

22:05.921 --> 22:07.280
and are safety hazards.

22:07.481 --> 22:09.241
You're part of my team now.

22:10.040 --> 22:14.120
I need to ensure both safety
and work quality for all my team.

22:14.441 --> 22:15.600
Understood?

22:19.921 --> 22:21.760
Earlier, people were praising you,

22:21.881 --> 22:23.241
calling you the 'female lead'.

22:24.161 --> 22:26.600
But that image doesn't match

22:26.600 --> 22:28.120
your actual mindset or taste.

22:28.600 --> 22:31.161
I choose shoes by their looks,

22:31.481 --> 22:33.360
not convenience.

22:39.320 --> 22:41.280
That's nouveau riche mentality.

22:41.760 --> 22:42.760
Sun Siwei.

22:42.800 --> 22:43.881
Siwei means thinking.

22:44.161 --> 22:45.241
With a name like that,

22:46.800 --> 22:48.560
you never use your brain.

22:49.881 --> 22:51.800
Your husband is a great catch.

22:52.001 --> 22:53.320
With so many options,

22:53.641 --> 22:56.201
why does he obey you blindly?

22:57.840 --> 22:59.800
Could there be something fishy?

23:03.520 --> 23:06.560
Could it be guilt compensation

23:07.961 --> 23:09.360
or creating smokescreens?

23:11.320 --> 23:12.560
You better watch out.

23:14.641 --> 23:15.401
Siwei,

23:16.001 --> 23:19.280
you know scumbag tactics so well.

23:20.161 --> 23:22.241
Is your boyfriend one?

23:22.921 --> 23:23.481
Yan,

23:23.760 --> 23:24.520
we're ready

23:24.560 --> 23:25.280
to film.

23:26.241 --> 23:27.080
Let's go.

23:33.241 --> 23:34.681
Dear viewers,

23:34.681 --> 23:35.320
hello.

23:35.360 --> 23:36.921
Welcome to Financial News.

23:36.961 --> 23:38.001
I'm your host, Xu Yan.

23:38.001 --> 23:39.201
(Jinda And Shouke
Build a Smart New District)

23:39.201 --> 23:42.520
After Jinda Group
and Shouke Real Estate's partnership,

23:42.600 --> 23:45.001
public attention remains high.

23:45.201 --> 23:48.161
Today, on behalf of both companies,
Mr. Shen Haoming,

23:48.280 --> 23:49.401
Jinda's representative,

23:49.681 --> 23:53.721
announced the development theme
and plan for Plot 178.

23:57.641 --> 23:58.280
Haoming.

23:59.040 --> 24:01.881
It's the cooperation agreement
my father drafted for the New District.

24:03.921 --> 24:04.760
Qualifications,

24:04.961 --> 24:05.961
responsibility division,

24:06.161 --> 24:07.040
collaboration model,

24:07.241 --> 24:08.120
construction plans,

24:08.280 --> 24:09.320
and risk sharing.

24:09.441 --> 24:11.560
I've highlighted key sections for you.

24:11.921 --> 24:12.560
Take a look.

24:17.560 --> 24:19.241
You're new to the industry,

24:20.161 --> 24:23.280
but your competence surprises me.

24:24.681 --> 24:27.201
Your approval means everything.

24:27.560 --> 24:28.481
To help you

24:28.760 --> 24:29.681
and this project

24:29.840 --> 24:30.961
is my goal.

24:31.560 --> 24:32.201
Next,

24:32.481 --> 24:33.600
I'll strive to do better.

24:37.280 --> 24:38.001
It's getting late.

24:38.560 --> 24:39.568
I'll drive you home.

24:39.840 --> 24:40.520
No need.

24:41.080 --> 24:42.192
I'm heading the other way.

24:43.921 --> 24:44.921
I'll get a ride-hail.

24:44.921 --> 24:45.721
It's convenient.

24:47.120 --> 24:50.681
And after making you
miss Xu Yan's birthday,

24:51.161 --> 24:53.840
I still feel guilty.

24:54.961 --> 24:55.721
I'm sorry.

24:56.001 --> 24:57.600
It's fine. It's all in the past now.

24:57.800 --> 24:58.360
Let's go.

25:06.401 --> 25:07.001
You okay?

25:07.241 --> 25:07.721
I'm fine.

25:07.721 --> 25:09.481
I skipped dinner.

25:09.481 --> 25:10.201
I'm feeling dizzy.

25:10.560 --> 25:11.201
Sit down.

25:12.360 --> 25:13.080
Thanks.

25:27.040 --> 25:27.800
Eat this.

25:34.520 --> 25:35.520
Take the whole box.

25:38.161 --> 25:39.241
You work late often.

25:39.760 --> 25:41.104
It's easy to get low blood sugar.

25:41.560 --> 25:42.721
Keep some sweets handy.

25:43.961 --> 25:44.560
Thank you.

25:49.401 --> 25:50.721
Take your time eating.

25:51.001 --> 25:52.001
I'll drive you home.

26:38.241 --> 26:38.921
Haoming,

26:40.080 --> 26:41.120
thanks for the ride.

26:42.201 --> 26:42.881
Don't mention it.

26:46.600 --> 26:47.241
Go up.

26:50.481 --> 26:52.241
After this project wraps up,

26:52.961 --> 26:54.641
can we go see a movie together?

26:57.681 --> 26:59.681
I just want a reward for myself.

27:00.040 --> 27:01.881
The approval from my superior.

27:05.001 --> 27:05.641
Okay.

27:06.360 --> 27:07.201
Pick a movie.

27:09.520 --> 27:10.161
Great.

27:11.641 --> 27:12.560
Bye, Haoming.

27:24.641 --> 27:25.840
Why do you have this?

27:26.320 --> 27:27.760
I've been looking everywhere for it.

27:28.840 --> 27:29.760
I found it.

27:41.721 --> 27:42.360
The reward.

28:01.760 --> 28:02.721
Bye, Haoming.

28:14.120 --> 28:14.840
Haoming.

28:18.120 --> 28:18.760
You're here.

28:19.080 --> 28:19.641
Yeah.

28:20.280 --> 28:21.360
Yan, you're here too.

28:21.721 --> 28:23.280
Feels like ages since I last saw you.

28:23.881 --> 28:25.201
I've been busy lately.

28:25.320 --> 28:26.201
I'm free today.

28:26.320 --> 28:27.520
I came to accompany Haoming.

28:31.201 --> 28:31.921
Are you alone?

28:33.840 --> 28:34.520
Let's play.

28:35.721 --> 28:36.560
Is that okay?

28:36.681 --> 28:38.161
Yan rarely gets to accompany you.

28:38.241 --> 28:39.840
Aren't you worried I'll crash your date?

28:40.360 --> 28:41.120
It's fine.

28:41.921 --> 28:43.520
Haoming wanted me to join him,

28:43.560 --> 28:44.481
but I can't grasp it.

28:44.721 --> 28:45.681
Perfect you came.

28:46.401 --> 28:47.040
Haoming,

28:47.280 --> 28:48.441
go easy on your sister.

28:49.681 --> 28:50.280
No need.

28:50.800 --> 28:52.840
We'll keep it fair since it's a match.

28:53.080 --> 28:54.001
No advantages taken.

28:56.401 --> 28:57.441
Which club first?

28:58.280 --> 28:59.120
Iron club.

28:59.280 --> 29:00.441
That suits me better.

29:01.600 --> 29:02.320
I'll go first.

29:17.201 --> 29:17.800
Nice shot.

29:19.161 --> 29:19.800
Haoming,

29:20.201 --> 29:21.161
are you free tonight?

29:21.881 --> 29:24.001
Let me treat you and Yan to dinner.

29:24.520 --> 29:26.641
I have a dinner
with Yuanhang Fund tonight.

29:28.320 --> 29:29.560
Why don't you join us?

29:30.441 --> 29:31.881
Mr. Yun, Mr. Liang,

29:32.001 --> 29:33.712
and their executive team
will be there too.

29:34.120 --> 29:35.921
They might ask technical questions.

29:36.241 --> 29:37.320
We can play off each other.

29:38.560 --> 29:39.481
I'll follow your lead.

29:44.161 --> 29:45.840
Let's have dinner together tonight.

29:47.481 --> 29:49.001
I'll skip the work dinner.

29:49.320 --> 29:49.840
Actually,

29:50.040 --> 29:51.441
I'm having dinner with my cousin.

29:51.481 --> 29:51.921
Okay.

29:52.201 --> 29:53.120
Careful, it's hot.

29:53.760 --> 29:54.641
How's the temperature?

29:54.921 --> 29:55.681
Just right.

30:00.280 --> 30:01.241
You've practiced a lot.

30:02.280 --> 30:03.280
Not really.

30:04.120 --> 30:06.040
Didn't you teach me everything I know?

30:06.280 --> 30:08.401
I never liked golfing in London.

30:10.201 --> 30:11.600
If you hadn't kept inviting me,

30:11.641 --> 30:12.800
I would've quit long ago.

30:13.001 --> 30:14.360
So thank you.

30:23.961 --> 30:24.760
No way.

30:24.840 --> 30:26.280
They could never be together.

30:26.961 --> 30:27.800
Keep your voice down.

30:29.961 --> 30:31.520
No matter what happens,

30:31.641 --> 30:33.800
he'd never fall for another woman.

30:34.040 --> 30:35.241
Even if every man cheated,

30:35.241 --> 30:36.241
he wouldn't. Understand?

30:36.560 --> 30:38.001
You've only met him a few times.

30:39.120 --> 30:40.201
Why trust him so much?

30:42.040 --> 30:43.721
True, I haven't seen him often,

30:44.241 --> 30:46.080
but I observe carefully each time

30:46.481 --> 30:47.481
and see it clearly.

30:47.600 --> 30:50.280
Every second, he only has eyes for you.

30:56.800 --> 30:59.001
But we used to share everything.

31:01.080 --> 31:07.721
Now it feels like glass separates us.

31:08.800 --> 31:10.040
We can see each other,

31:11.681 --> 31:13.080
but can't get closer.

31:15.161 --> 31:17.161
Maybe you're overthinking?

31:17.481 --> 31:19.721
Look, he's a businessman

31:20.120 --> 31:21.360
working around clock.

31:21.520 --> 31:23.161
Maybe he's just tired.

31:23.800 --> 31:24.401
Right?

31:25.921 --> 31:27.760
We finally got together today.

31:27.760 --> 31:28.280
Forget him.

31:28.320 --> 31:28.840
Let's drink.

31:40.560 --> 31:41.921
Haoming,

31:42.840 --> 31:44.520
don't you think I'm great?

31:45.201 --> 31:49.641
Today I finally got Jiang Yun
and Jiang Liang into signing for you.

31:50.441 --> 31:52.560
Our efforts finally paid off.

31:53.441 --> 31:54.120
You did great.

31:54.560 --> 31:55.840
You acted very professionally.

31:57.360 --> 31:58.320
Well done.

31:58.881 --> 31:59.840
I'll get you some water.

32:06.320 --> 32:07.161
Haoming,

32:08.921 --> 32:10.201
take a good look at me.

32:15.241 --> 32:16.481
I grew up long ago.

32:22.896 --> 32:24.336
(Yan)

32:41.264 --> 32:42.288
(Chen Lin)

32:47.481 --> 32:48.760
Can you not answer that?

32:49.721 --> 32:50.320
It's Chen Lin.

32:52.401 --> 32:53.280
Then answer it.

32:56.840 --> 32:57.401
Hello?

32:58.600 --> 32:59.441
It's done.

33:00.201 --> 33:00.681
The photo

33:00.760 --> 33:01.560
is sent to you.

33:01.760 --> 33:02.201
Okay.

33:16.181 --> 33:17.680
(Signatures)

33:19.921 --> 33:21.360
Why show me this?

33:21.721 --> 33:22.961
Mr. Huang and your father

33:23.441 --> 33:24.840
just signed the contract in the US.

33:25.721 --> 33:27.481
Good thing your father is on my side.

33:28.280 --> 33:30.441
Or the New District project
wouldn't materialize.

33:32.961 --> 33:35.241
Well he's my father.

33:35.441 --> 33:36.721
Naturally he supports

33:38.120 --> 33:39.840
the person I like.

33:44.641 --> 33:45.961
Thank him for me.

33:46.800 --> 33:47.840
Get some rest early.

33:48.961 --> 33:49.881
Shen Haoming,

33:50.560 --> 33:51.481
what are you doing?

33:55.040 --> 33:57.201
Now it's truly settled.

33:58.120 --> 33:59.280
You performed excellently.

34:00.120 --> 34:03.080
You'll be very pleased
with this year's bonus.

34:03.721 --> 34:04.360
Stop.

34:06.520 --> 34:09.420
Were you nice to me

34:11.440 --> 34:13.200
just to win over my father

34:14.200 --> 34:15.281
and keep me in check?

34:20.600 --> 34:22.600
You've been putting on an act with me.

34:24.001 --> 34:25.321
Can't call it an act.

34:26.520 --> 34:27.801
Just to keep you stable

34:29.361 --> 34:30.881
and prevent your occasional outbursts.

34:32.040 --> 34:32.841
Shen Haoming!

34:33.040 --> 34:34.040
I love you so much.

34:34.481 --> 34:35.720
You think I'm a lunatic?

34:36.120 --> 34:37.321
I'll tell Xu Yan

34:37.680 --> 34:38.441
and my father

34:38.441 --> 34:39.361
about what you've done.

34:40.720 --> 34:41.401
Suit yourself.

34:42.801 --> 34:44.040
If you dare walk out that door,

34:44.120 --> 34:45.520
I won't let you off.

34:47.160 --> 34:48.841
I'm begging you, Haoming.

34:49.001 --> 34:50.080
I didn't mean to.

34:50.080 --> 34:51.240
Don't be angry.

34:51.520 --> 34:52.080
Mr. Shen.

34:56.841 --> 34:57.321
Han Weiping,

34:57.321 --> 34:58.200
why are you here?

34:58.680 --> 34:59.881
Let me reintroduce you.

35:00.640 --> 35:01.520
Han Weiping,

35:02.441 --> 35:05.441
former senior corporate lawyer
at Jinda Group,

35:06.600 --> 35:08.520
now my private attorney.

35:08.921 --> 35:10.001
You've worked hard lately.

35:10.361 --> 35:11.881
Take your time with the follow-ups.

35:12.040 --> 35:12.801
Don't worry.

35:12.881 --> 35:13.841
I'll handle it properly.

35:14.001 --> 35:15.040
What do you mean?

35:15.481 --> 35:16.600
Why did you lie to me?

35:16.600 --> 35:18.080
Explain yourself.

35:19.240 --> 35:20.200
Go away.

35:20.200 --> 35:21.401
Go!

35:23.881 --> 35:24.761
Had enough drama?

35:26.600 --> 35:27.160
You...

35:27.841 --> 35:29.481
All of you are liars.

35:30.520 --> 35:32.720
It was all a setup from the beginning.

35:32.761 --> 35:33.801
You trapped me.

35:34.600 --> 35:37.720
You think signing means victory?

35:38.520 --> 35:39.761
I won't forgive any of you.

35:40.040 --> 35:41.640
Especially you, Han Weiping.

35:42.001 --> 35:42.680
Miss Fang,

35:43.401 --> 35:44.801
as a professional lawyer,

35:45.321 --> 35:46.881
I advise against escalating conflicts.

35:47.881 --> 35:48.680
What?

35:49.600 --> 35:50.640
Scared now?

35:51.240 --> 35:52.080
I'm not scared.

35:52.801 --> 35:53.921
I want to tell you.

35:54.321 --> 35:55.801
You tried to wreck Mr. Shen's family.

35:56.240 --> 35:57.200
For every thing you did

35:57.200 --> 35:58.160
and every word you said,

35:58.881 --> 36:01.600
I have all evidence and recordings.

36:06.640 --> 36:07.600
So I advise you.

36:07.961 --> 36:09.001
You're still young.

36:10.040 --> 36:12.120
You need reputation
for future endeavors.

36:23.921 --> 36:25.240
You were my client after all.

36:25.841 --> 36:26.961
I'll let it slide this time.

36:27.520 --> 36:28.520
If there's a next time,

36:29.080 --> 36:30.441
you'll face legal consequences.

36:30.761 --> 36:31.640
Get some rest.

37:14.720 --> 37:15.481
It's late.

37:15.921 --> 37:16.680
Still awake?

37:25.120 --> 37:25.841
I'm expecting you.

37:28.401 --> 37:29.720
Why didn't you answer your phone?

37:31.321 --> 37:32.961
I had something important to handle.

37:33.761 --> 37:35.120
So I didn't call back. Sorry.

37:43.520 --> 37:44.160
Haoming,

37:46.841 --> 37:48.281
I need to tell you something.

37:49.160 --> 37:54.240
If it's something that'll make me happy,

37:54.761 --> 37:55.560
go ahead and say it.

37:59.680 --> 38:01.361
If it'll upset me,

38:05.321 --> 38:06.640
don't say a single word.

38:11.801 --> 38:12.761
I'm a bit tired.

38:13.600 --> 38:14.441
I need to rest.

39:10.640 --> 39:11.401
Yan.

39:17.881 --> 39:18.680
Why are you here?

39:20.921 --> 39:22.160
I'm here to pick up Haochen.

39:22.321 --> 39:23.801
Why are you picking up Haochen?

39:25.520 --> 39:26.600
Does this need a reason?

39:28.921 --> 39:30.200
I'm his biological aunt.

39:36.441 --> 39:37.801
What scheme are you plotting now?

39:39.761 --> 39:40.680
This is a school.

39:42.441 --> 39:43.640
Control yourself and leave.

39:44.361 --> 39:45.040
Yan,

39:47.361 --> 39:49.001
actually, every time I face you,

39:50.281 --> 39:52.080
I feel really guilty inside.

39:53.401 --> 39:54.520
Also, I found out

39:55.001 --> 39:56.600
you've been kept in the dark.

39:58.120 --> 39:59.001
I think this situation

39:59.200 --> 40:00.560
is very unfair to you.

40:02.600 --> 40:06.881
Actually, Haoming and Haochen
aren't brothers at all.

40:09.080 --> 40:10.401
They're father and son.

40:20.801 --> 40:22.881
When Haoming was studying in London,

40:23.401 --> 40:24.520
he dated my sister.

40:25.160 --> 40:27.640
My sister got accidentally pregnant
and gave birth to Haochen.

40:28.680 --> 40:30.441
But they were still young back then,

40:30.600 --> 40:31.600
only twenty years old.

40:32.281 --> 40:34.401
My sister made me keep it
from our father.

40:35.520 --> 40:39.560
So the baby was taken
by the Shens immediately after birth.

40:41.160 --> 40:45.321
Shen Jinsong and Yu Lan were worried
about an illegitimate child scandal.

40:46.040 --> 40:47.961
Fortunately, not many people
knew about it.

40:48.481 --> 40:50.641
To the public, they said

40:51.664 --> 40:53.321
(it's Haoming's younger brother.)

40:54.560 --> 40:58.961
Later, my sister died
in a diving accident.

41:00.961 --> 41:04.441
That made this matter
a permanent secret.

41:12.841 --> 41:15.881
The three of us are blood-related.

41:16.321 --> 41:17.600
No one can change that

41:17.640 --> 41:18.961
or sever that bond.

41:19.481 --> 41:20.560
In this world,

41:20.761 --> 41:24.040
no one could accept Haochen
more sincerely than me.

41:29.281 --> 41:30.640
You probably didn't know this.

41:31.040 --> 41:32.281
On your birthday,

41:34.040 --> 41:35.321
Haoming was at my place.

41:38.240 --> 41:39.321
You didn't answer my call.

41:39.321 --> 41:40.640
I feared something happened.

41:40.841 --> 41:41.361
I'm fine.

41:41.921 --> 41:43.881
Shifeng and Jinda
are signing an agreement.

41:43.961 --> 41:44.921
We had a meeting.

41:45.281 --> 41:46.680
So I put my phone on silent.

41:48.761 --> 41:50.281
He probably didn't tell you

41:50.520 --> 41:52.520
what we did together, did he?

42:07.481 --> 42:09.481
Unless Shen Haoming tells me himself,

42:12.240 --> 42:13.680
I won't believe anything you say.

42:15.761 --> 42:17.841
You... you don't think

42:17.921 --> 42:23.040
your relationship with Haoming
is some pure romance, do you?

42:31.441 --> 42:33.600
From the start,
he wasn't looking for a wife.

42:33.801 --> 42:37.640
He wanted a name
to put on a marriage certificate.

42:39.120 --> 42:41.130
You just happened to appear

42:41.130 --> 42:43.001
(in his sight at that time.)

42:43.720 --> 42:45.080
But my philosophy is

42:46.921 --> 42:49.321
I must shape it into what I like.

42:54.801 --> 42:56.441
You're not from matching social status,

42:58.120 --> 42:59.401
but you're fairly clever

42:59.961 --> 43:00.921
and ambitious.

43:01.600 --> 43:03.080
You've become a host lately,

43:03.401 --> 43:05.761
which perfectly serves
to promote his business

43:05.921 --> 43:06.761
and his character.

43:07.361 --> 43:10.600
I wonder if we could have the honor
of Xu Yan interviewing you.

43:12.680 --> 43:14.921
Consider it
giving the new host a chance.

43:21.321 --> 43:23.200
A seemingly perfect family

43:23.761 --> 43:26.841
can gain him much trust
from business partners.

43:28.240 --> 43:30.401
Plus you're obedient and sensible.

43:31.520 --> 43:33.281
Even knowing he has a child,

43:34.240 --> 43:35.881
you'd still let him control you.

43:37.001 --> 43:40.361
It'd be a perfect
and rational choice for him.

43:42.401 --> 43:43.040
By the way,

43:44.361 --> 43:48.921
you actually thought you became a host
through your own ability?

43:50.120 --> 43:52.001
He put in great effort

43:52.240 --> 43:53.921
to get you that host position.

44:05.489 --> 44:06.896
Bye bye!

44:06.896 --> 44:08.987
- Bye.
- Bye, sir!

44:13.961 --> 44:14.640
Sis-in-law?

44:16.361 --> 44:17.321
Sis-in-law.

44:25.761 --> 44:27.001
(Haochen is your brother.)

44:27.160 --> 44:28.361
(We're family.)

44:28.720 --> 44:31.520
(It's only natural for us
to care for each other.)

44:31.640 --> 44:32.961
(You've done well.)

44:33.160 --> 44:34.401
Thank you, sis-in-law.

44:39.720 --> 44:42.801
(Haochen has been spoiled
ever since he was born.)

44:43.200 --> 44:45.040
(His temper grew worse and worse.)

44:45.281 --> 44:48.720
(I never expected
you'd get along so well with him.)

44:49.560 --> 44:51.961
(I think he genuinely likes you.)

